{"tid":498848,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"余光中病逝　終年89歲","createTime":"2017-12-14T07:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T08:44:10.000Z","uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba30aacd300912d1ef6b17c2f101e344004bb25f","tid":498848,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"著名文學家余光中在台灣高雄病逝，終年89歲。<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒報道，余光中於一個多月前，曾出席中山大學為他慶祝的生日聚會，是他最後一次公開露面。他日前懷疑輕微中風及肺部感染入院。<br />\n<br />\n余光中1928年在南京出生，以現代詩和散文著名，代表作包括詩集《白玉苦瓜》、散文集《記憶像鐵軌一樣長》等。國共內戰期間，跟隨家人移居香港，並於1950年到台灣定居，並於1974年開始擔任本港中文大學中國語言及文學系教授，85年返回台灣，出任中山大學文學院院長。"},{"pid":"3b4f4080ba615a8580602b44dd5cfcd60f13f1e2","tid":498848,"uid":139716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1370039-20171214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1370039-20171214.htm&d=y%2Fqd8MyStx9%2BQdFqO2ApWtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=18943f2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1370039-20171214.htm&h=ec4ea06d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1370039-20171214.htm</a>"},{"pid":"96b8ffe4a34d5273a2b49ff80e2ad958290f6394","tid":498848,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e531e7b01ec465d159460e3cf7bb9f8c454ba33","tid":498848,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rip吧"}]}